<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span><span class="c4">[٢]</span> وَعَبْدٍ.<a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p2"></span><span class="c4">[٣]</span> وَامْرَأَةٍ.<a href="#p2" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p3"></span><span class="c4">[٤]</span> وَفَقِيرٍ عَاجِزٍ عَنْهَا <span class="c2">(١)</span>.<a href="#p3" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p4"></span><span class="c4">[٥]</span> وَنَحْوِهِمْ.<a href="#p4" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p5"></span>- وَيَلْزَمُ أَخْذُهُمْ بِحُكْمِ الإِسْلَامِ فِيمَا يَعْتَقِدُونَ تَحْرِيمَهُ مِنْ نَفْسٍ، وَعِرْضٍ، وَمَالٍ، وَغَيْرِهَا.<a href="#p5" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p6"></span>- وَيَلْزَمُهُمْ التَّمَيُّزُ عَنِ المُسْلِمِينَ.<a href="#p6" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p7"></span>- وَلَهُمْ رُكُوبُ غَيْرِ خَيْلٍ بِغَيْرِ سَرْجٍ.<a href="#p7" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p8"></span>-<span class="c5"> وَحَرُمَ:</span><a href="#p8" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p9"></span>- تَعْظِيمُهُمْ.<a href="#p9" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p10"></span>- وَبُدَاءَتُهُمْ بِالسَّلَامِ.<a href="#p10" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p11"></span>- وَإِنْ تَعَدَّى الذِّمِّيُّ عَلَى مُسْلِمٍ، أَوْ ذَكَرَ اللهَ، أَوْ كِتَابَهُ،<span class="c5"> أَوْ رَسُولَهُ بِسُوءٍ:</span><a href="#p11" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p12"></span>- انْتَقَضَ عَهْدُهُ.<a href="#p12" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p13"></span>- فَيُخَيَّرُ الإِمَامُ فِيهِ كَأَسِيرٍ حَرْبِيٍّ.<a href="#p13" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<hr>
<p class="hamesh">(١) قوله: (عنها) سقطت من (د).</p> </div>